            <title>[OPENJPA-972] Support standard provider properties in PersistenceProvider class</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OPENJPA-972</link>
                <project id="12310351" key="OPENJPA">OpenJPA</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Implement support for PU properties and hints passed in persistence.xml and/or the Map parameter of createEntityManagerFactory().&lt;br/&gt;
Section 8.1.3.1 of the JPA 2.0 Public Draft #1.&lt;br/&gt;
This work item is to add junit coverage on Query for the following new PU properties:&lt;br/&gt;
   javax.persistence.lock.timeout&lt;br/&gt;
   javax.persistence.query.timeout&lt;br/&gt;
Supplying them in a Map to createEMF should override any values supplied in persistence.xml.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
